---
import Layout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="content-inner">

    <h1>About</h1>

    <h2>CVAMO</h2>

    <p>
      CVAMO (Cost, Value Analytics, Models &amp; Optimization) is a research lab
      bringing together professors and pre- and postdoctoral researchers from
      diverse departments associated with the Business Engineering program at
      the Faculty of Economics and Business Administration, Ghent University.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our team has extensive expertise in Industrial Management and focuses on
      addressing engineering challenges from business and economic perspectives.
      Our research activities span several key domains in analytics, decision
      support, and operations.
    </p>

    <h2>Faculty of Economics and Business Administration</h2>

    <p>
      CVAMO is embedded in the Faculty of Economics and Business Administration
      at Ghent University. The faculty combines strong economic and managerial
      expertise with quantitative and analytical methods to address complex
      challenges in business and industry.
    </p>

    <div class="about-block">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Machineries &amp; Factories (M&amp;F)</h2>

        <p>
          CVAMO is part of Machineries &amp; Factories (M&amp;F), an industrial
          research platform bringing together the activities of around 125
          researchers from different research groups across several faculties
          at Ghent University and Howest.
        </p>

        <p>
          M&amp;F research contributes to the development of smart motion
          products and smart production systems in an Industry 4.0 environment
          driven by digitalization and digital twin technologies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-logo">
        <img src="/images/mf_logo.jpg" alt="Machineries & Factories logo" />
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="about-block">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>Flanders Make</h2>

        <p>
          CVAMO is a core lab of <strong>Flanders Make</strong>, the Strategic
          Research Centre for the manufacturing industry.
        </p>

        <p>
          Based on high-tech research, Flanders Make actively supports companies
          in the manufacturing industry in developing and optimizing products
          and production processes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-logo">
        <img src="/images/fm_logo_new.png" alt="Flanders Make logo" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>
